    "updated_at": "2026-03-10T09:38:08Z",
    "body": "`right_format` is (currently) always rendered with native shell facilities and the alignment is not controlled by starship.\n\nYou may be able to improve alignment by adding trailing spaces to the first line of your prompt. Please also ensure that you are using an UTF-8 locale, to avoid issues with non-ansi text.",
