    "body": "you can remove the additional whitespace by setting `ZLE_RPROMPT_INDENT=0`\nsee [this superuser.com post](https://superuser.com/questions/655607/removing-the-useless-space-at-the-end-of-the-right-prompt-of-zsh-rprompt)",
